{"lemma":"تَلّ","slug":"تَلّ","root":"ت.ل.ل","root_slug":"ت-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ت-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"تَلّ","root":"تلل","pos":"V","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":14},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4005","n4013"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of تَلَّ (talla) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"heap of sand, hillock, mound, knob"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hill, elevation"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pillow","tags":["rare"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to throw (someone) down on their neck, cheek or forehead"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to throw into difficulties"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to throw or push (something) into one's hand"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to humble oneself, to fawn"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fall down"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to pour out"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to drop with perspiration"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to let down"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to take by the hand"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lead a beast of burden"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *tall- (“hill”)."},"ipa":["/tall/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4005","headword_ar":"تَلٌّ","root":"tl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Lth, [and accord. to general present usage,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hill, of dust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rubbish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pressed together, not natural:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but this is a mistake [if meant as an explanation of the proper application], for with the Arabs it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a natural hill:"},{"kind":"text","text":"En-Nadr says that"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is of the smaller sort of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ikaAm","text_ar":"اـِكَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamapN","text_ar":"اَكَمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is of the height of a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the breadth of its back is about ten cubits;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is smaller than the A^akamap, has fewer stones, gives growth to nothing good, and its stones are compacted together exactly like those of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) [the mound, or artificial hill, above mentioned, is what is meant by its being said,] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tal~","text_ar":"تَلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of dust, or earth, is well known: and the word signifies also a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heap"},{"kind":"text","text":"of sand: (M, K:*) in both of these senses from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~al~u","text_ar":"التَّلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ the throwing upon the ground ” anything of a corporeal kind: (M:) also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hill"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overtopping what is adjacent to it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atolaAlN","text_ar":"اَتْلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atul~N","text_ar":"اَتُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tilaAlN","text_ar":"تِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuluwlN","text_ar":"تُلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pillow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atolaAlN","text_ar":"اَتْلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is extr.: or the pl. signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"certain sorts of cloths,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of garments:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of pillows."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","M","K","TA","S","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n4013","headword_ar":"تَلٌّ","root":"tl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an imitative sequent to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl~N","text_ar":"ضَالٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, * S, M, * K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}